# Python Conventions

- Formatter: **Black** (default config)
- Indent: 4 spaces
- Type hints: optional, encouraged in new code
- Imports: stdlib → third-party → local (one blank line between groups)

## VulnBank Specifics

- App entrypoint: `labs/vulnbank/app.py`
- Routes go in `labs/vulnbank/app/routes/` (when modularized)
- Templates in `labs/vulnbank/app/templates/`
- Mark vulnerabilities: `# VULN: [category] - [description]`
- Document in `labs/vulnbank/vulns/VULNERABILITIES.md`
- Tests in `labs/vulnbank/tests/test_vulns.py`
- Dependencies: `labs/vulnbank/requirements.txt` (pin versions)
- Virtual env: `.venv/` (already gitignored)

## Testing

```bash
cd labs/vulnbank && pytest tests/
```
